import React from 'react'; import { Table, TableBody, TableCell, TableContainer, TableHead, TableRow, Button, Tab } from '@mui/material'; const CourseTable = ({ currentItems, handleClickOpen }) => ( Course ID Course Address Course Title Course Instructor Course Date Course Start Time Course End Time Course Is Active Actions {currentItems.map((course) => ( {course.id} {course.address} {course.date} {course.startTime} {course.endTime} ))}
); export default CourseTable;
